cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a dialog agent for robots that can interpret user commands using a semantic parser and improve its language capabilities through dialog experiences. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper involves developing a learning agent for robots that can improve its knowledge base and language capabilities. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is another likely category as the paper focuses on developing a dialog agent for robots and evaluating it on real-robot platforms. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper involves developing a learning agent for robots. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves developing a software system for human-robot dialog.
